title: Semen Klyuchyk
text:
Semen Leonidovych Klyuchyk (; born 23 December 1997) is a Ukrainian <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for Ukrainian side <a href="AFSC%20Kyiv">AFSC Kyiv</a>.
Career.
Klyuchyk is a product of FC Metalurh Zaporizhzhia youth team system. His first trainer was Dmytro Vysotskyi.
He made his debut for <a href="Metalurh%20Zaporizhzhia">Metalurh Zaporizhzhia</a> in the <a href="Ukrainian%20Premier%20League">Ukrainian Premier League</a> in a match against <a href="FC%20Volyn%20Lutsk">FC Volyn Lutsk</a> on 29 November 2015.
